    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Weiseronyssus persicus n. sp., female: 1, idiosoma, dorsal aspect; 2, gnathotectum, anterolateral aspect; 3, genua II, dorsal aspect; 4, tarsus IV, ventral aspect." ;
